[{"id":"edcc9fa0c24d1eeca91eecd76e4aa65b","from":"Lookout Mobile Security","from_email":"feedback@email.lookout.com","to":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to_list":[{"name":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"Heartbleed security vulnerability - what you need to know","date":"2014-04-11T14:31:21.000Z","formatted_date":"Apr 11, 2014","formatted_time":"2:31 PM","body":" Lookout Notice\nhttps://www.lookout.com/ \n\nOn Monday, a serious security vulnerability in OpenSSL - software which two-thirds of the Internet uses to keep connections secure - was announced and nicknamed \"Heartbleed.\" This vulnerability allows an attacker to steal sensitive data (such as account information and passwords) from various web services and clients.\n\n\nWe want all of our users to know that Lookout's website was not affected by the vulnerability, however, some of Lookout's other Internet-facing infrastructure was. We took care to protect our users as soon as possible, patching our systems and replacing all of our SSL certificates within hours of the bug's public release. \n\n\nHowever, because two-thirds of all active websites depend on OpenSSL to communicate securely, some of the other services you use may not be patched yet.\n\n\nHow can you protect yourself?\n\nLook out for communications from the services you use. As companies patch this vulnerability and secure their own systems, some may send emails or other communications to let you know. Not all services will be communicating about this vulnerability, but you can always contact them to ask if their systems are secure. \n\nGet a new password ready. If you receive communications from any of your service providers telling you that their systems are secure, this is the best time to change your password. Changing your password before a system is secure could actually make your new password easier to intercept.\n\nTo learn more about the Heartbleed vulnerability, you can read our blog post for more details: https://blog.lookout.com/blog/2014/04/09/heartbleed/.\n\n\n- The Lookout Team\n\nhttps://www.lookout.com/?utm_source=internal&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=lookoutnotice \nLearn more about Lookout \n\n(c) 2014 Lookout, Inc. \u2219 One Front St. Suite 2700 \u2219 San Francisco, CA 94111\n\nhttps://www.lookout.com/d/settings \nUnsubscribe  \u2219 \nhttps://www.lookout.com/legal/privacy \nPrivacy  \u2219 \nhttps://www.lookout.com/legal/terms \nTerms and Conditions \n\n\n\n \n","body_html":"</body></html><!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n  <head>\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\" />\n    <title>Lookout Notice</title>\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n    <style type=\"text/css\">\n      #outlook a {padding:0;} body{width:100% !important; -webkit-text-size-adjust:100%; -ms-text-size-adjust:100%; margin:0; padding:0;}\n      .backgroundTable {margin:0; padding:0; width:100%;}\n      img {text-decoration:none; -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;} img a, a img {border:0px!important;}\n      span.autoLinks a {color: #ffffff!important; text-decoration: none!important;}\n      span.preheader {font-size: 0; line-height: 0; display: none;}\n      table {border-collapse: collapse;}\n      p {margin:0; padding:0; margin-bottom:0;}\n      .emailCopy p {margin: 0px 0px 0px 0px;}\n      .emailCopy a, .emailArticleHeading a, .emailImageHeading a, .emailButtonHeading a, .emailHeadline a {color: #000000; text-decoration: none;}\n      @media screen and (max-device-width: 550px), screen and (max-width: 550px) {\n      \tbody {padding: 0px!important;width:100%!important;}\n      \t*[class=\"emailDisplayFullWidth\"] {width: 100%!important; min-width: 100%!important; max-width: 100%!important; border: none!important; height: auto;}\n      \t*[class=\"emailSection\"] {}\n      \t*[class=\"emailTopBar\"] {padding: 20px 20px!important;}\n       .emailHeadline-green { font-size:25px!important; line-height:35px!important;}\n       .emailHeadline-blue { font-size:25px!important; line-height:35px!important;}\n      .secondaryHeader-text { font-size:18px!important; line-height:28px!important;}\n      }\n</style>\n</head><body bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-left: 0; padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; padding-right: 0; padding-left: 0; min-width: 100%; width: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\n  \n    <span class=\"preheader\" style=\"display:none!important;font-size:0;line-height:0;\"></span>\n    <table class=\"backgroundTable\" width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-left: 0; padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; padding-right: 0; padding-left: 0; width: 100%;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <table class=\"emailDisplayFullWidth\" width=\"620\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\">\n\n            <tr>\n  <td class=\"emailTopBar\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" width=\"100%\" style=\"padding-top: 22px; padding-bottom: 20px; padding-right: 30px; padding-left: 30px; border-bottom: 6px solid #eee; text-align: center;\">\n    <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"width:100%!important;border-collapse:collapse;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"color:#aeaeae;font-family:'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;padding-top:1px;padding-bottom:0;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;\" align=\"center\">\n          <a href=\"https://www.lookout.com/\" style=\"color: #3db249; text-decoration: none; font-size: inherit; font-weight: inherit; border: none; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif;\">\n            <font color=\"#aeaeae\">\n              <img label=\"Logo\" class=\"logo\" src=\"https://image.email.lookout.com/lib/fe9915707362077c70/m/1/lookout-logo.png\" alt=\"Lookout Mobile Security Logo\" title=\"Lookout Mobile Security Logo\" height=\"40\" width=\"200\" style=\"display: block; text-decoration: none; -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic; border-width: 0;\" />\n            </font>\n          </a>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </td>\n</tr>\n            <tr>\n  <td class=\"emailSection\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #ddd; text-align: center; width: 100%; max-width: 620px;\">\n    <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"10\" cellspacing=\"0\" align=\"center\" class=\"header-table\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td class=\"emailHeadline-green\" align=\"center\" style=\"font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-weight: 400; text-align: center; color: #3db249; font-size: 38px; line-height: 50px;\">\n          <font face=\"'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n\n    \t\t\t</font>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </td>\n</tr>\n            <tr>\n  <td height=\"10\">\n  </td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n  <td class=\"mainEmailSection\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" valign=\"top\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%; max-width: 620px;\">\n    <table class=\"main\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" align=\"center\" style=\"border: 0; padding: 0; margin: auto; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; width: 100%; max-width: 620px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n      <tr>\n  <td>\n    <table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"10\" class=\"emailBody\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" style=\"text-align: left; color: #5b5b5b; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; width: 100%; max-width: 620px; font-size: 1.15em; line-height: 1.5em;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td align=\"center\" class=\"emailBody-text\" style=\"helvetica: neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; padding: 0 20px; text-align: left;\">\n          <font face=\"'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;\">\nOn Monday, a serious security vulnerability in OpenSSL - software which two-thirds of the Internet uses to keep connections secure - was announced and nicknamed \"Heartbleed.\" This vulnerability allows an attacker to steal sensitive data (such as account information and passwords) from various web services and clients.<br>\n<br>\nWe want all of our users to know that Lookout's website was not affected by the vulnerability, however, some of Lookout's other Internet-facing infrastructure was. We took care to protect our users as soon as possible, patching our systems and replacing all of our SSL certificates within hours of the bug's public release. <br>\n<br>\nHowever, because two-thirds of all active websites depend on OpenSSL to communicate securely, some of the other services you use may not be patched yet.  <br>\n<br>\nHow can you protect yourself?<br>\n          </font>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </td>\n</tr>\n\n    </table>\n  </td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n  <td height=\"10\">\n  </td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n  <td class=\"mainEmailSection\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" valign=\"top\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%; max-width: 620px;\">\n    <table class=\"small-main\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" align=\"center\" style=\"border: 0; padding: 0; margin: auto; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; width: 80%; max-width: 540px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"10\" class=\"emailBody\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" style=\"text-align: left; color: #5b5b5b; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; width: 100%; max-width: 620px; font-size: 1.15em; line-height: 1.5em;\">\n            <tr>\n              <td align=\"center\" class=\"emailBody-text\" style=\"helvetica: neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; padding: 0 20px; text-align: left;\">\n                <font face=\"'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;\">\n<strong>Look out for communications from the services you use.</strong> As companies patch this vulnerability and secure their own systems, some may send emails or other communications to let you know. Not all services will be communicating about this vulnerability, but you can always contact them to ask if their systems are secure. <br>\n<br>\n<strong>Get a new password ready.</strong> If you receive communications from any of your service providers telling you that their systems are secure, this is the best time to change your password. Changing your password before a system is secure could actually make your new password easier to intercept.<br>\n<br>\n\n                </font>\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n          </table>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n  <td height=\"10\">\n  </td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n  <td class=\"mainEmailSection\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" valign=\"top\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%; max-width: 620px;\">\n    <table class=\"main\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" align=\"center\" style=\"border: 0; padding: 0; margin: auto; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; width: 100%; max-width: 620px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n      <tr>\n  <td>\n    <table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"10\" class=\"emailBody\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" style=\"text-align: left; color: #5b5b5b; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; width: 100%; max-width: 620px; font-size: 1.15em; line-height: 1.5em;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td align=\"center\" class=\"emailBody-text\" style=\"helvetica: neue,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; padding: 0 20px; text-align: left;\">\n          <font face=\"'helvetica neue', helvetica, sans-serif;\">\nTo learn more about the Heartbleed vulnerability, you can read our blog post for more details: https://blog.lookout.com/blog/2014/04/09/heartbleed/.<br>\n<br>\n- The Lookout Team<br>\n<br>\n\n          </font>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </td>\n</tr>\n\n    </table>\n  </td>\n</tr>\n\n            <tr>\n   <td>\n    <table class=\"footer\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"border: 0; padding: 0; margin: auto; width: 100%; max-width: 620px; text-align: center; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n      <tr>\n  <td>\n    <table cellpadding=\"10\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"learn-more\" border=\"0\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"border: 0; padding: 0; margin: auto; width: 100%; max-width: 650px; font-size: 16px; text-align: left; border-top: 1px solid #e1e1e1; border-bottom: 1px solid #e1e1e1; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td colspan=\"2\" valign=\"middle\">\n          <span class=\"link\" style=\"max-width: 100%; margin: auto; text-align: left; color: #3db249; font-size: 1.2em; padding: 0; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://www.lookout.com/?utm_source=internal&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=lookoutnotice\" class=\"green\" style=\"text-decoration: none; font-size: inherit; font-weight: inherit; border: none; font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #3db249;\">Learn more about Lookout</a></span>\n        </td>\n\n      \n    </table>\n  </td>\n</tr>\n\n      <tr>\n  <td>\n    <table cellpadding=\"10\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"finePrint\" border=\"0\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"border: 0; padding: 0; margin: auto; width: 100%; max-width: 620px; text-align: center; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n      <tr>\n        <td class=\"finePrintCopy\" style=\"text-align: center; margin: auto; 